description: Prior Approval under Class MA, Part 3 of Schedule 2 to the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) (Amendment) Order 2015 (as amended in 2024) for the proposed change of use of the existing vacant office accommodation at Lewisham House, 25 Molesworth Street, SE13 to provide 193 residential dwellings.
application_type_full: Prior Approval: Change of use from Commercial, Business and Service (Use Class E) to Dwellinghouses (Use Class C3)
